**Job Summary**

We are currently looking for a Customer Service Representative to join our team in Secaucus, NJ. This person will assist clients by providing new and existing clients outstanding service via telephone, chat and/or email. Their principal duties are to demonstrate excellent analytical and problem-solving skills while explaining complex technical concepts to our customers.

**Duties & Responsibilities**

* Answer inbound calls and emails from customers regarding products ordered through the website;
* Assist customers with the proper use of our products and guide them through the online ordering process;
